headline: Is Rollins' 33.6% Rally Justified After Recent Expansion News?
summary: Ever wondered if Rollins is fairly priced right now or if there is an opportunity hiding beneath the surface? You are in the right place for a deep dive into its value. The shares have caught a serious tailwind lately, jumping 14.2% over the last month and climbing 33.6% year-to-date. This shows strong momentum that is hard to ignore. Recent headlines have highlighted strategic expansion in new service areas and the company’s ongoing acquisition activity. Both have energized investor...
